==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Indicant
<hw>In"di*cant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>indicans</ets>, p. pr. <ets>indicare</ets>. See
<er>Indicate</er>.]</ety> <def>Serving to point out, as a remedy;
indicating.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Indicant</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Indicant
<hw>In"di*cant</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That which indicates or points
out; <as>as, an <ex>indicant</ex> of the remedy for a
disease</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Indicate</ent>⟦br⟧
